c:=c||'ssions</strong> option to the appropriate value, based on the type of page. &nbsp;For example, it should be set to <strong>No</strong> for DML forms and <strong>Yes</strong> for most other types of pages.</li>'||chr(10)||
'	<li>If setting it to <strong>No</strong>, then optionally supply a URL to redirect users to in the case of a duplicate page submission.</li>'||chr(10)||
'	<li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li>'||chr(10)||
'</ol>'||chr(10)||
'';

sv_sec_import.attribute(
