'<p>'||chr(10)||
'	The goal for any developer is to fix as many of the identified issues as possible. However in some cases there are reasons to leave settings as they are. For this purpose, <strong>sumnevaSERT</strong> provides developers with the ability to submit and track <a href="#">Exceptions</a> to the rules out';

